Create a Network-Wide Ad Blocker with a Raspberry 

 If you want to block ads on all your devices—from your smartphone to your tablets—you’ll need something a little stronger. Enter the Pi-Hole, a Raspberry
 Pi image that blocks ads of all sorts at the router level.
 This project is the geart easy and cheap way to block all the Ads from the net work for all the devicecs at the same time.
